(The selected dataset is **TissÈo ? RÈseau transport urbain toulousain**. TissÈo Voyageurs) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(produces transport data for the Toulouse urban network. The static GTFS describes the) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(theoretical public-transport offer: stops, schedules, and lines. It is published daily and) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(covers approximately the next three weeks.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
