() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(## Why start with static GTFS?) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(Static GTFS is finite, file-based, reproducible, and easy to inspect. It gives this first) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(phase a clear foundation for raw-data preservation, metadata, and data-quality profiling) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(before any continuously changing inputs are introduced.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(TissÈo also publishes GTFS-RT real-time data. It is postponed because real-time ingestion) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(introduces polling, changing state, and operational concerns that are outside this phase. No) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(GTFS-RT data is downloaded or processed here.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
