(# Static GTFS KPI definitions) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(These gold indicators describe the **planned transport offer** in TissÈo's static schedule.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(## Scheduled trips by route and day) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(One row represents one route on one service date. `scheduled_trips_count` counts trips whose) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(`service_id` is active that day. This is the main first-version KPI because it makes planned) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(route supply easy to compare across dates.) Tj
ET
