0 -11.00 Td
(# Real-time snapshot KPI definitions) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(These indicators are computed from one parsed GTFS-Realtime Trip Updates snapshot and one) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(static silver GTFS run.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(## Feed health) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(`rt_feed_health_snapshot.csv` describes the snapshot itself: feed type, fetch time, header) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(timestamp, feed age, entity counts, identifier counts, and whether delay fields are present.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(Freshness status:) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(- PASS: feed age is 90 seconds or less;) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(- WARN: feed age is over 90 seconds and up to 300 seconds;) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(- FAIL: feed age is over 300 seconds;) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(- UNKNOWN: feed age cannot be computed.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(This is a snapshot health indicator, not a service-level guarantee.) Tj
