() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(# Mobility Control Tower) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(Mobility Control Tower is a local data-engineering project that turns public-transport data) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(into explainable planning indicators. The current static MVP preserves and profiles TissÈo) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(static GTFS, creates bronze and cleaned silver tables, validates them, builds gold static) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(planning KPIs, generates PNG charts, and writes teacher-facing Markdown evidence reports. It) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(also includes a bounded GTFS-Realtime snapshot exploration layer.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(## Dataset) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(This phase uses the daily static GTFS for the TissÈo urban network. It represents the) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(theoretical offer \(stops, routes, trips, and schedules\) for approximately the next three) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(weeks under the ODbL licence. See [docs/data_source.md]\(docs/data_source.md\).) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
