() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(## Install) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(Python 3.10 or newer is required.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(```bash) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m venv .venv) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(source .venv/bin/activate) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m pip install -e '.[dev]') Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(```) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(## Run) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(For the dependable manual workflow, place `Tisseo_GTFS.zip` in `data/raw/manual/`, then run) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(the commands below. Replace `<run_id>` with the timestamp printed by ingestion.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(```bash) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli ingest-gtfs --source tisseo --local-zip) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(data/raw/manual/Tisseo_GTFS.zip) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli profile-gtfs --raw-run data/raw/tisseo/<run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli build-bronze --raw-run data/raw/tisseo/<run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli build-silver --bronze-run data/bronze/tisseo/<run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli validate-gtfs --silver-run data/silver/tisseo/<run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli build-gold --silver-run data/silver/tisseo/<run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli generate-static-charts --gold-run) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(data/gold/tisseo/<run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli generate-demo-report --gold-run) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(data/gold/tisseo/<run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli generate-static-mvp-report --gold-run) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(data/gold/tisseo/<run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(```) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(Automatic download from the source URL configured in `config/sources.yml` is also supported:) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(```bash) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli ingest-gtfs --source tisseo --download) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(```) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(Ingestion creates an immutable ZIP and metadata under `data/raw/`. Bronze preserves selected) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(GTFS text files. Silver produces cleaned CSV tables. Gold produces schedule KPI tables under) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(`data/gold/`. Each layer has a manifest. Profiling, validation, charts, the demo report, and) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(the static MVP evidence report are generated under `data/reports/`.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(The current MVP is intentionally static: it proves a reproducible Data Engineering flow from) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(a public GTFS ZIP to validated analytical tables and evidence artifacts. It does not use) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(GTFS-RT and does not measure actual delays, cancellations, or passenger waiting time. See) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
([docs/runbook.md]\(docs/runbook.md\), [docs/data_quality.md]\(docs/data_quality.md\),) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
([docs/kpi_definitions.md]\(docs/kpi_definitions.md\), and) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
([docs/static_mvp_explanation.md]\(docs/static_mvp_explanation.md\).) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(## GTFS-Realtime snapshot exploration) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(This project can fetch one GTFS-Realtime protobuf snapshot, preserve it as `feed.pb`, parse) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(it into CSV files, report feed freshness and identifiers, and compare live identifiers with) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(static silver GTFS tables.) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(```bash) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli fetch-gtfs-rt --source tisseo --feed-type trip_updates) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli parse-gtfs-rt --raw-rt-run) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(data/raw_realtime/tisseo/trip_updates/<rt_run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli report-gtfs-rt --rt-run) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(data/realtime/tisseo/trip_updates/<rt_run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli check-rt-compatibility \\) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(  --silver-run data/silver/tisseo/<static_run_id> \\) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(  --rt-run data/realtime/tisseo/trip_updates/<rt_run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli build-rt-gold \\) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(  --silver-run data/silver/tisseo/<static_run_id> \\) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(  --rt-run data/realtime/tisseo/trip_updates/<rt_run_id>) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(python -m mobility_control_tower.cli generate-rt-charts --rt-gold-run) Tj
ET
endstream
