(## Local DuckDB serving layer) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
() Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(DuckDB is used as a local SQL serving layer because it does not require a server and can) Tj
0 -11.00 Td
(load the generated CSV data products. Build a queryable database from static gold outputs,) Tj
